==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Haje
<hw>Ha"je</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧"j⟦esl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar.
<ets>hayya</ets> snake.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The Egyptian asp
or cobra (<spn>Naja haje</spn>.) It is related to the cobra of India,
and like the latter has the power of inflating its neck into a hood. Its
bite is very venomous. It is supposed to be the snake by means of whose
bite Cleopatra committed suicide, and hence is sometimes called
<altname>Cleopatra's snake</altname> or <altname>asp</altname>. See
<er>Asp</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hake</ent>⟦br⟧
